query:
SELECT
            u."id" as id
            FROM "Macrotation" ma
            INNER JOIN "Document" d ON d.id = ma."documentId"
            INNER JOIN "UserHistory" uh ON uh."itemId" = d."id" AND uh."itemType" = 'document'
            INNER JOIN "User" u ON u.id = uh."userId"
            WHERE ma.id = $1 AND u.id != ma."userId"
